   ```
   All six changes to `symbology.ts`, all three changes to `planElementMeshBuilders.ts`, the Python functions in `engine.py`, and the test file have been re-applied. The implementation is complete but NOT yet verified (tests not re-run) and NOT yet committed/pushed.

